data.description: This well maintained home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, radiating comfort and care. Adorned with charming landscaping, it enjoys a convenient location and offers a host of appealing amenities. Outside, an expansive above-ground pool is complemented by a deck, creating a tranquil space for relaxation and entertainment. A thoughtfully finished shed adds versatility? serving as an extra bedroom or an ideal home office, tailored to your needs. Inside, the home impresses with its condition and ambiance. Step onto the covered rear deck for open-air dining or unwind on the front deck, watching the world go by. Practicality meets convenience with a 2-car carport, while additional parking for RVs, boats, and more. In summary, this home presents a blend of comfort, versatility, and location. Don't miss the chance to make it yours!
